summary: This appears to be an email transmitting multiple FBI 302 (interview report) documents related to the Epstein investigation in New York. The email itself is a cover note forwarding several attached PDF files of FBI reports.
keyFacts: The document is an email dated April 23, 2020, forwarding multiple FBI 302 reports.
The attached files are FBI 302 documents from the New York investigation into Jeffrey Epstein, identified by case number 050D-NY-3027571.
The email subject indicates these are '302s (2 of 3)', suggesting this is part of a batch of FBI interview summaries.
